				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$P_g \eta_p = p_g \mu_g \eta_g \eta_p \geq P_s$$\end{document}

When ηg decreases due to a drop of the amount of ambient energy the generator is able to extract from the environment, then the system will cease to function correctly, i.e. when ηg<Pspgμgηp.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
