				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\eta_g < \frac{P_s}{p_g \mu_g \eta_p}.$$\end{document}

When n generators are attached to the power conditioning circuitry, this introduces n (largely) independent efficiencies ηg:
3ηp∑k=1npgkμgkηgk≥Ps.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
