				\begin{document}$$\eta_p \sum_{k=1}^n \int\limits_{T_1T_2} p_{g_k} \mu_{g_k} \eta_{g_k} dt \geq \int\limits_{T_1T_2} P_s dt$$\end{document}

Using the previously described elaborated regime model, the following simplification is derived:
8ηp∑k=1n∫T1T2pgkμgkηgkdt≥T1T2Pactived+Psleep(1-d)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
